ygData.messageBody:
> xaera - level 50 SK as of 2 days ago
> moods - level 50 Cleric as of 3 days ago

Both these players were pushed through the game by numerous
L50s powering them. And I dont mean the occasional assist,
they sat around and were given all the exp they wanted. If
I had L50s setting me up with that kinda of exp I'd be 50
already. No real glory in those two accomplishments. I
admire their primary toons, but those twinks are nothing
to be much proud of imo.

Harmonic.
